<!-- ══════ WEBSITE ══════ -->
<h1>Website</h1>
<hr class="rule">

<div class="done"><strong>Pre-launch site is live</strong> — meridianhealth.com.au is password-protected and live. No changes needed until the August launch sprint.</div>

<h2>Full launch — mid-August 2026</h2>
<ul class="check">
  <li>Content and copy review across all pages — streamline, refine tone</li>
  <li>Interior/clinic photography shoot — images needed before go-live</li>
  <li>Replace placeholder images with real photography</li>
  <li>Layout refinements (post-copy-review)</li>
  <li>Remove password gate</li>
  <li>Remove prelaunch page / redirect to home</li>
  <li>Submit sitemap to Google Search Console</li>
  <li>Confirm all page meta titles and descriptions are final</li>
</ul>

<div class="note">Pre-launch page stays live and password-protected until the August launch date. No public search engine indexing until then (noindex header already in place for prelaunch).</div>


<!-- ══════ BREVO ══════ -->
<h1>Brevo — patient communication system</h1>
<hr class="rule">

<div class="done"><strong>All email copy is written</strong> — 9 individual emails + 15 pathway track emails (Tracks 10A–10E) are complete and paste-ready in the reference docs.</div>
<div class="done"><strong>Website form → Brevo integration is built and deployed</strong> — the Netlify serverless function is live. BREVO_API_KEY is set. Submissions will flow as soon as the IP whitelist is cleared.</div>

<h2>What still needs to happen (in order)</h2>

<table class="t">
  <tr><th>#</th><th>Action</th><th>Where</th><th>Owner</th><th>Blocker?</th></tr>
  <tr>
