    <span style="font-size:10pt;color:#555">Brevo → Settings → Authorised IPs → add <span class="path">34.138.234.101</span> and <span class="path">34.73.105.70</span></span></td>
    <td>Brevo security settings</td>
    <td class="owner">Brevo admin</td>
    <td style="color:#c0392b;font-weight:700">Yes — unblocks everything below</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>2</td>
    <td><strong>Create 7 contact attributes + 9 tags</strong><br>
